ic_en", "text": "becoming like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qubayoTaA='", "text_ar": "قُبَيْطَا=ء"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.], (M,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and is used medicinally as a remedy for roughness of the chest and for pain of the fauces:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, TA:) or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gum of a certain tree called the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kamokaAm", "text_ar": "كَمْكَام"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e. the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cancamum-tree"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "brought from El-Yemen:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) or this is a mistake, for it is the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "tree so called, not its gum:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) [but] it is said in the T, on the authority of AHn, that"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kamokaAm", "text_ar": "كَمْكَام"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the bark ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qirof", "text_ar": "قِرْف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") of the tree called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Dirow", "text_ar": "ضِرْو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and some say that it is the resin ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eilok", "text_ar": "عِلْك"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Dirow", "text_ar": "ضِرْو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and in the Moheet of Ibn-'Abbád it is said that"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kamokaAm", "text_ar": "كَمْكَام"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the bark ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qirof", "text_ar": "قِرْف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or, as some say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "liHaA='", "text_ar": "لِحَا=ء"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",) of the tree called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Dirow", "text_ar": "ضِرْو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and is an aromatic perfume: (TA:) and (K, TA) IAar says, (TA,) the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Dirow", "text_ar": "ضِرْو"}, 